{"query":"query persons($skip: Int, $take: Int) {
  persons(skip: $skip, take: $take) {
    id
    username
    email
    roles
    createdDate
    metaData
    metaDataInternal
    mobilePhone
    postal
    city
    region
    geoLocation
    timezone
    personalInfo
    profile
    fundsBalance {
      debit
      credit
      balance
    }
    volunteeringHoursBalance {
      debit
      credit
      balance
    }
    goodsStock {
      id
      code
      barCode
      name
      description
      tags
      balance {
        debit
        credit
        balance
      }
      metaData
      metaDataInternal
      createdDate
      createdByPersonId
    }
    firstName
    lastName
    gender
    height
    fatherFirstName
    fatherLastName
    motherFirstName
    motherLastName
    birthDate
    nationality
    country
    documentNumber
    documentType
    cardVersion
    emissionDate
    expirationDate
    emittingEntity
    identityNumber
    fiscalNumber
    socialSecurityNumber
    beneficiaryNumber
    pan
    requestLocation
    otherInformation
    registrationDate
  }
}
","variables":{"skip":0,"take":50},"operationName":"persons"}

{"query":"query personById($id: String!){
  personById(id: $id) {
      # non citizenCard data
      id
      username
      mobilePhone
      email
      attributes {
        id
        content
        issuedDate
        expiresDate
        expired
        certifierID
      }
      roles
      participant {
        id
        name
        msp
      }
      createdDate
      metaData
      metaDataInternal
      # extended non citizenCard data
      mobilePhone
      postal
      city
      region
      geoLocation
      timezone
      personalInfo
      profile
      # balance
      fundsBalance{
        debit
        credit
        balance
      }
      volunteeringHoursBalance{
        debit
        credit
        balance
      }
      goodsStock {
        id
        code
        barCode
        name
        description
        tags
        balance{
          debit
          credit
          balance
        }
        metaData
        metaDataInternal
        createdDate
        createdByPersonId        
      }
      # citizenCard data    
      firstName
      lastName
      gender
      height
      fatherFirstName
      fatherLastName
      motherFirstName
      motherLastName
      birthDate
      nationality
      country
      documentNumber
      documentType
      cardVersion
      emissionDate
      expirationDate
      emittingEntity
      identityNumber
      fiscalNumber
      socialSecurityNumber
      beneficiaryNumber
      pan
      requestLocation
      otherInformation
      registrationDate
  }
}","variables":{"id":"{{ personIdJohn }}"},"operationName":"personById"}

{"query":"mutation personAddAttribute($personId: String!, $addPersonAttributeData: AddPersonAttributeInput!) {
  personAddAttribute(personId: $personId, addPersonAttributeData: $addPersonAttributeData) {   
      # non citizenCard data
      id
      username
      email
      attributes {
        id
        content
        issuedDate
        expiresDate
        expired
        certifierID
      }
      roles
      participant {
        id
        name
        msp
      }
      # extended non citizenCard data
      mobilePhone
      postal
      city
      region
      geoLocation
      timezone
      personalInfo
      profile
      # citizenCard data    
      firstName
      lastName
      gender
      height
      fatherFirstName
      fatherLastName
      motherFirstName
      motherLastName
      birthDate
      nationality
      country
      documentNumber
      documentType
      cardVersion
      emissionDate
      expirationDate
      emittingEntity
      identityNumber
      fiscalNumber
      socialSecurityNumber
      beneficiaryNumber
      pan
      requestLocation
      otherInformation
      registrationDate    
  }
}
","variables":{"personId":"{{ personIdJane }}","addPersonAttributeData":{"id":"dead-year","content":{"data":"1971","work":true},"issuedDate":1554239270,"certifierID":"{{ participantIdGov }}"}},"operationName":"personAddAttribute"}
